{
  "stem": "4830.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the procession of Jewish doctors is their knowledge.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And this, he could put into service for the Hungarian people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But there was no time to organize all this so he just organized this one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now of course, in addition to the doctors, there was need for a supporting staff.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And this is how we got in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now the hospital initially had a very small number of beds.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Around 100 beds, or even less.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But as the war continued, we developed a major role in treating the wounded.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And there were many wounded people, civilian and from the military.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we were growing-- the supply came from the fascist storage headquarter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we were reasonably supplied with food-- what they had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And of course, this mainly went to him and to the doctors, who were, of course, considered to be the most important.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I was very much impressed as I had nothing, really, to eat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Nothing very substantial.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There was, up until the last 10 days, there was a central kitchen, where they had some food for the members of the staff.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But [INAUDIBLE] through this [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Bergessi ?] told me that he has somewhere-- about three kilometers from this place where we were in the basement of a house, two big sticks of salami.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And if I bring it to him, he will give me one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So I went during the siege, and you could imagine that of course [INAUDIBLE] was not an easy thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I got there, I found it, and I brought it back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he told me that he changed his mind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And he doesn't give me from the salami.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But instead of that, he will give me his book that he wrote, that the soul is everything, and he will autograph it for me.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
